### 4.5 [app.py](file:///d:/Major_project/app.py) — Flask Web Application

The web server that ties everything together.

**4 Web Pages:**

| Page | Route | What it shows |
|---|---|---|
| Dashboard | `/` | System overview — CPU, memory, disk charts |
| Training | `/training` | Train models from the UI, view accuracy/F1/AUC results |
| Monitoring | `/monitoring` | Live detection feed with ransomware alerts |
| About | `/about` | Project documentation & methodology |

**8 API Endpoints:**

| Endpoint | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `GET /api/system-status` | Current CPU/memory/disk metrics |
| `GET /api/detect` | Runs one detection cycle, returns prediction |
| `GET /api/model-info` | Returns trained model name, features, metrics |
| `GET /api/model-results` | All 15 model evaluation results |
| `POST /api/train` | Triggers full training pipeline |
| `GET /api/detection-history` | Last N detection results |
| `GET /api/hpc-events` | List of HPC event names |
| `GET /api/io-events` | List of I/O event names |

